APT - Searching Packages

Use [prgm]apt search[/prgm] to find packages by name or description.

$ [prgm]apt search[/prgm] [arg-value]keyword[/arg-value]                       # Search names and descriptions
$ [prgm]apt search[/prgm] [arg]--names-only[/arg] [arg-value]keyword[/arg-value]  # Search names only
